%%{init: {'theme':'neutral', 'themeVariables': {'fontSize':'15px'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Client
    participant PC as PolicyCache
    participant Map as store · HashMap
    participant Pol as LruEvictionPolicy
    participant DLL as LinkedKeyList
    participant Obs as EvictionListener

    Note over Client,Obs: get(key) — a read that mutates recency
    Client->>PC: get(key)
    PC->>Map: containsKey(key)?
    alt hit
        Map-->>PC: true
        PC->>Pol: recordAccess(key)
        Pol->>DLL: moveToFirst(key)
        PC->>Map: get(key)
        Map-->>PC: value
        PC-->>Client: value
    else miss
        Map-->>PC: false
        PC-->>Client: null
    end

    Note over Client,Obs: put(key, value) — insert / update / evict
    Client->>PC: put(key, value)
    alt key already present
        PC->>Map: put(key, value)
        PC->>Pol: recordAccess(key)
        Pol->>DLL: moveToFirst(key)
    else new key
        opt size == capacity
            PC->>Pol: evict()
            Pol->>DLL: removeLast()
            DLL-->>Pol: victim
            Pol-->>PC: victim
            PC->>Map: remove(victim)
            PC->>Obs: onEvict(victim, oldValue)
        end
        PC->>Map: put(key, value)
        PC->>Pol: recordInsertion(key)
        Pol->>DLL: addFirst(key)
    end
    PC-->>Client: void
